plot: &"1888: The Extraordinary Voyage of The Santa Isabel&" is a whimsical adventure fantasy about a tired Jules Verne, fleeing from Paris and a bored wife, who joins Italian explorer Stradelli in an expedition on the Orinoco river. Along the way they pickup a young stranger- a woman disguised as a man, searching for her lost father.   Written by  Anonymous
title: 1888, el extraordinario viaje de la Santa Isabel
